  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Victims of crime: letter from the Home Secretary to Mayor of Greater Manchester
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Home Secretary, Rt Hon Priti Patel MP, writes to Mayor of Greater Manchester, Andy Burnham, about an inspection of the service provided to victims of crime.</p>

  </div>
</div>

